Keywords: Pragmatism, institution, traction, emotion, transformation. JEL Classification: B25, B40. 1. INTRODUCTION The influence of pragmatism on institutionalism and the role of
rules and habits in decision-making1, whether by Thorstein Veblen (1990; 1970; 1946) or John Commons (1934; 
